Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.41,0:01:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在雪中散去的再不斩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来这里干吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带了这么多人又是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.81,0:01:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我改主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.27,0:01:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思了 再不斩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.02,0:01:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请你死在这儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果请正规忍者 可是要花很多钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.78,0:02:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才会雇佣你们这些叛忍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能顺便让你们这些忍者互相残杀的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以节约我很多金钱和时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么雾隐鬼人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我眼里不过是个滑稽的小丑罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙从哪儿冒出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.81,0:02:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西 抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然我不用去杀达兹纳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再跟你打下去也没意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子跟我还有点有过节呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:02:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然害本大爷骨折
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 这小子已经死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋 想干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要轻举妄动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是开口说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是你的同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的遗体被那样糟蹋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一点感觉都没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.84,0:03:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了他一直伴随在你左右吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就像是卡多在利用我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也只是在利用白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.77,0:03:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们忍者只不过是工具
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的 是他的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是他的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…毫无依恋…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.57,0:03:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…真的这么想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.97,0:03:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们与他的战斗已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还是我的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打从心底喜欢你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.16,0:04:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有很重要的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是那么地喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当一个人一心想保护重要的东西时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就真的可以变强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的一点感觉都没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要成为真正的忍者是很难的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的完全不在乎他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.11,0:04:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想实现他的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.25,0:04:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此 我愿意成为真正的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想变得像你一样厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是却只得到这种结果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.12,0:05:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…为了你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.18,0:05:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连自己的命都不要了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要实现他的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.23,0:05:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…就是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连自己的梦想也没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能像工具一样死去…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.27,0:05:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这实在是太残酷了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再说下去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白不只是为了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.46,0:06:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是为了你们才决意要战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比谁都清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是个老好人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够跟你们交手真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.61,0:06:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者也是人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许无法成为没有感情的工具…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我输了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.71,0:06:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 把你的苦无借给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你们快去干掉那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为靠自己一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能打赢这么多人吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼…鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你既然那么想见同伴的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.57,0:08:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就自己一个人去吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没打算…跟白去同一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么…你还想逞强…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和本大爷一起…下地狱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾隐鬼人下了地狱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以变成真正的鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我究竟是不是小丑到地狱就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.71,0:10:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了…白…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路走来 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别转头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一个努力活下去的男人最后的尊严
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小樱…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小樱 你好重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐…助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.61,0:11:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.55,0:11:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小樱…好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.24,0:11:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了 小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不可以动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 鸣人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那个戴面具的家伙呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那个戴面具的少年已经死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.38,0:11:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被鸣人杀了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.37,0:11:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他为了掩护再不斩…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都相信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是佐助 躲过了致命伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.76,0:11:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙打从一开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小樱…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助没事了 他还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.17,0:12:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白也是为了你们才决意要战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.76,0:12:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是个老好人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下放心了 佐助也平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们开心得太早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们好不容易找到的雇主就这么被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 我们干脆袭击城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把值钱的东西都拿走好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一下子就能解决这些人的忍术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.86,0:12:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我消耗了太多的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们敢再靠近这座岛一步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.23,0:13:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就要动用所有的武力了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.71,0:13:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们有来无回
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊那利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄总是迟一些登场的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊那利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伙们…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我也来助你们一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身之术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.65,0:13:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种程度的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我现在的查克拉也能虚张声势一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身之术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西版
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊 动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西 有件事想拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.69,0:14:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…再看看那家伙的脸…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种季节竟然会下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哭泣吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了 卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来 你都在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:16:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少…最后时刻让我能在你身边…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.98,0:16:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的…想和你去同一个地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是出生在一个白雪皑皑的村子里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就像雪一样洁白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的 再不斩…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们会在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 卡卡西老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.07,0:17:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者存在意义真的像他们说的一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.29,0:17:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以追寻自身存在的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要像工具那样存在才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点连我们木叶也不例外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓真正的忍者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.62,0:17:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也这么想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.33,0:17:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以忍者都不知觉地活在这个困扰中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像再不斩和那个孩子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走我自己的忍道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.21,0:18:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一条绝对不会后悔的路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇往直前地走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.84,0:18:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托各位的福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大桥已经建成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来会非常寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请保重
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢各位的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.93,0:18:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:18:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达兹纳大叔 我还会再来玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊那利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也会觉得很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想哭就哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.29,0:19:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人哥哥才是 想哭就哭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.41,0:19:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 就爱逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个少年改变了伊那利的心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊那利改变了村民的心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个少年为我们搭建了迈向希望的勇气之桥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桥啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:19:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到桥的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没给大桥取名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然想到一个超级适合这座桥的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫“鸣人大桥”如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.76,0:20:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要赶快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让伊鲁卡老师请我吃拉面庆祝任务完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 还有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让木叶丸知道我的英勇事迹才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.32,0:20:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 回村之后跟我约会好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.59,0:20:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我约会吧 我随时奉陪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.16,0:20:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了 鸣人 你给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要取这个名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望这座大桥永远都不会垮掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.97,0:21:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且有一天会成为举世闻名的大桥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.52,0:21:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要叫这个名字啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.71,0:22:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.06,0:22:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们第七班最近老是执行一些简单的任务啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.00,0:23:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们明明打败了\N像再不斩和白那样厉害的忍者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.32,0:23:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没什么更能让我施展身手的任务吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.68,0:23:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我的忍道和心都燃烧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.10,0:23:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.94,0:23:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的篇章 晋级中忍的考试
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.36,0:23:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的忍道